[{"question":"What do we know about the person that perpetrated this hideous crime?","answer":"You know, it is so heart-breaking, Piers.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":24,"aSentId":25},{"question":"What can you do?","answer":"Well, obviously it\u0027s been a horrific day in the greater Danbury area and particularly the town of Newtown.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":79,"aSentId":80},{"question":"Did you know if there plans for more vigils tomorrow?","answer":"There are vigils scheduled throughout this community, Newtown, throughout weekend.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":96,"aSentId":97},{"question":"When was the first you heard about this and how did you hear?","answer":"I received a call from the school system from the superintendent saying that there was a shooting in Newtown, but didn\u0027t say it was a school, that the schools were on lockdown.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":110,"aSentId":111},{"question":"When you got there, obviously scenes of complete chaos, how quickly was it that you realized your daughter was safe?","answer":"OK.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":115,"aSentId":116},{"question":"Can you hear?","answer":"Not really.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":127,"aSentId":128},{"question":"Is this something you could have predicted he would one day flip and do something as monstrous as this?","answer":"I don\u0027t know if you can ever predict something like that would happen.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":164,"aSentId":165},{"question":"Was he sociable?","answer":"I always saw him alone when he was walking through the school or when he was sitting at the table, or sitting on the bus.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":180,"aSentId":181},{"question":"How would you describe his personality?","answer":"He was really quiet.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":184,"aSentId":185},{"question":"Did you know his family, his mother in particular?","answer":"I mean, I knew her because we lived in the neighborhood.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":190,"aSentId":191},{"question":"Were you aware of that having a big impact on him?","answer":"I don\u0027t know when they got divorced.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":198,"aSentId":199},{"question":"What was your immediate reaction when you discovered it was this person you knew?","answer":"It was devastating.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":207,"aSentId":208},{"question":"When was the last time you spoke to Adam Lanza?","answer":"Probably middle school.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":229,"aSentId":230},{"question":"What is the possible background to what is going on here?","answer":"You know, working on a lot of these cases, there a number of different causes that can be divided into two broad categories.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":261,"aSentId":262},{"question":"Are people like this as likely to carry out what they end up doing, these atrocities, if they didn\u0027t have easy access to firearms?","answer":"Look, there is no question that firearms play a role.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":272,"aSentId":273},{"question":"Where do you start with trying to counsel young children when this kind of appalling thing happens?","answer":"I think the first thing is helping the parents.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":279,"aSentId":280},{"question":"Why he would then, having killed his mother, go to the school and do what he did?","answer":"You know, I don\u0027t have a crystal ball and I haven\u0027t diagnosed or assessed him.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":301,"aSentId":302},{"question":"Frank?","answer":"I\u0027d like to endorse that also.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":331,"aSentId":332},{"question":"What would you like to see in terms of specific gun control?","answer":"Well, there a number of pieces of legislation that we have been pushing for years.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":417,"aSentId":418},{"question":"Can I follow-through on the Australia thing?","answer":"ORGAN: No, I want you to answer this.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":445,"aSentId":446},{"question":"Allowing, therefore, a clearly deranged son to take them and commit this atrocity?","answer":"Whatever that gun looks like, it\u0027s a semiautomatic rifle.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":449,"aSentId":450},{"question":"It\u0027s time for change?","answer":"Right, it is time.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":460,"aSentId":461},{"question":"Time to do what?","answer":"To get rid of some of these gun laws that cause --","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":462,"aSentId":463},{"question":"To get rid of the gun laws?","answer":"Look at what has happened, all these attacks this year have occurred where guns are banned.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":464,"aSentId":465},{"question":"What has that got to do with it?","answer":"You never let me explain.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":469,"aSentId":470},{"question":"Can I say something?","answer":"-- gun-free zone.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":471,"aSentId":472},{"question":"Is that right?","answer":"Well, I believe those of us who are licensed to carry, are responsible people, shouldn\u0027t be prohibited from carrying in schools or other places.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":504,"aSentId":505},{"question":"Why on Earth would you want more guns in schools after what happened today?","answer":"Here\u0027s why, Piers.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":507,"aSentId":508},{"question":"What were your feelings?","answer":"It\u0027s -- it\u0027s impossible to put words to what I really feel.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":612,"aSentId":613},{"question":"Do you wish after what happened to you and to Josh that tougher laws had been brought in after that to try and do something about this?","answer":"You know, I do.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":621,"aSentId":622},{"question":"What do you think?","answer":"You know, to be honest, it\u0027s heartbreaking.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":631,"aSentId":632},{"question":"What are your views about the debate that will now unfold on this?","answer":"I mean, I think the president said we need a meaningful action now.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":649,"aSentId":650},{"question":"What do you feel today?","answer":"I think in the wake of today, a referendum on guns is needed.","docId":"121214pmt","qSentId":666,"aSentId":667}]